gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 119, Warriors 103
gameRecap.excerpt: Nikola Jokic tallied the 18th triple double of his season with 32 points, 16 rebounds, and 16 assists as the Nuggets defeated the Warriors, 119-103. Jamal Murray (27 points, four rebounds, three assists) and Aaron Gordon (17 points, six rebounds) totaled 44 points. Klay Thompson (23 points) and Stephen Curry (20 points) led Golden State in the loss. The Nuggets win their third straight game to improve to 39-19 as the Warriors move to 29-27.
